        "DataValidation": "Require updated global LNG demand and supply forecasts (2025\u20132027) before final investment authorization.",
        "FiscalSafeguards": "Set diversification investment targets (\u226525% of incremental LNG revenue) to reduce hydrocarbon dependency.",
        "Monitoring": "Mandate quarterly pattern-detection and risk reports to the Energy and Finance Ministries.",
        "ReviewTrigger": "Reassess strategy if global LNG demand growth falls below 2% annually for two consecutive years or if carbon-pricing regimes materially penalize LNG imports."
      }
    }
  }
}

